data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite property that exudes taste and charm at every turn. Situated in a highly sought-after location, this home boasts a plethora of luxurious features that are sure to captivate the most discerning buyer.
As you step through the grand entrance, you are immediately greeted by a sense of coziness. The open floor plan seamlessly blends modern design with farmhouse elements, creating a harmonious atmosphere that is both inviting and sophisticated. The upgraded floor coverings throughout the home confirm the great taste of the decorator.
The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, adorned with pristine quartz countertops and new, updated backsplash. The upgraded tile in the bathrooms and showers adds a touch of elegance, transforming every bathing experience into a spa-like retreat.
Escape to the master suite, a sanctuary of tranquility and relaxation. Indulge in the luxuriousness of the  magnificent shower and upgraded quartz.
The attention to detail is evident in the mix of painted and stained woodwork, adding depth and character to every room.
In addition to the four true bedrooms and four full bathrooms, this home also features a bonus room that includes one of the full baths and closet, providing endless possibilities for customization. Whether it be a home office, a media room, or a guest suite, the possibilities are limited only by your imagination.
Step outside and discover your very own outdoor living space, complete with tiled concrete and an upgraded privacy fence that ensures your moments of relaxation remain uninterrupted.
This property offers the convenience of a neighborhood park and pool, providing endless opportunities for recreation and leisure. Additionally, its prime location offers easy access to Moore, Norman, OKC, and Tinker, ensuring that you are never far from the vibrant energy of the city.
